tweet: Disappointing that all of the complaints are on the side of reducing the revenue.  That said, there is a bit difference between ditching this policies and tinkering with them.  Corp rate of 26%, capita gains rate of 30%, and carry-over basis for farms would still get lots of $$.
name: Marc Goldwein - GET VAXXED!

tweet: It speaks volumes that there was nothing in the Government's #QueensSpeech about supporting British farming.  Conservatives have abandoned farmers, and their policies have put the future of hundreds of small family farms at risk.  Only @LibDems will stand up for British farming.
name: Tim Farron
